verses.1: Gimna na thuak ciangin Topa in nang hong en henla, Jakob始 Pasian in nangmah hong dal tahen!
verses.2: Siangtho mun panin huhna nang hong puak henla, Zion panin nang hong panpih tahen!
verses.3: Na biakpiaknate khempeuh amah in hong phawk henla, na meihal biakpiakna hong sang tahen!
verses.4: Na lungsim始 deihna amah in hong pia henla, na geelna khempeuh hong tangtungsak tahen!
verses.5: Na gualzawhna ah eite lungdamin awngin, i Pasian始 min tawh i lante khai ni!
verses.6: Topa in a sathau nilh pa a huh ding tu-in ka thei ta a, ama vantung siangtho panin amah dawng dinga, a vangliatna tawh amah gualzosak ding hi.
verses.7: Mi pawl khat in leengte kisaktheih pih a, mi pawl khat in sakolte kisaktheih pih hi. Ahih hangin eite in Topa i Pasian始 min bek i kisaktheih pih hi.
verses.8: Amaute kinawmsawmin puk gawp ding uh a, ahih hangin eite tho-in i ding tang ding hi.
verses.9: Topa aw, kumpipa tungah gualzawhna pia inla, kong sap ciangun hong dawng in.
